author: ggregory
msg: org.apache.logging.log4j.core.LogEvent.getContextMap() should never return null. Remove the getContextMap(String) API (aka getContextMapValue(String). The FlumeEvent is a little different and can indeed hold a null context map. All tests pass from Maven.
